<center><h1 id="amaranth">The Euroleague Response to COVID-19</h1></center>
<br>
<br>
<center><p id="titillium">Due to the need to keep fans, participants and game staff safe during the COVID-19 global pandemic, Turkish Airlines EuroLeague teams will begin the 2020-21 season with restrictions on attendance at their games.</p></center>
    <br>
    <center><p id="titillium">The restrictions depend on national and/or local health guidelines that all Euroleague Basketball clubs are committed to fulfilling in order to help ensure the safe environments required to ultimately defeat the coronavirus.</p></center>
